WEBVTT

00:00.083 --> 00:02.827
The Republic of Florence...
is excommunicated.

00:02.828 --> 00:05.207
Neither the Pope
or King Ferrante

00:05.208 --> 00:07.576
will receive any diplomatic
envoy from Florence.

00:07.644 --> 00:09.145
But they will receive me.

00:09.212 --> 00:11.347
I would have spared Amelia
if I could.

00:11.415 --> 00:14.684
Don't you dare speak
her name! Don't you dare!

00:14.751 --> 00:18.254
I've got no ship, no astrolabe,
no map that explains it all

00:18.322 --> 00:20.189
and Nico - he's with Riario.

00:20.257 --> 00:23.392
If you think I'll help you find the
Vault of Heaven, I'd die first!

00:23.460 --> 00:25.561
There must be a way
to follow Riario and Nico.

00:25.629 --> 00:27.196
<i>Your only hope</i>
<i>is the Sentinel.</i>

00:27.264 --> 00:31.500
And the chaos of slave rebellion
would help us seize command.

00:31.568 --> 00:34.036
I'm drawn to recall
that day from our youth

00:34.104 --> 00:37.473
when you held me beneath
the icy waters...

00:37.541 --> 00:39.175
The Pope holds a prisoner.

00:39.242 --> 00:41.744
A man about whom
you care deeply.

00:41.812 --> 00:45.781
What are you?
The one true hope.

